        "management": "Central line required (PICC, subclavian, IJ). Infusion through dedicated port. Maximum dextrose 25% final concentration. Start at 50% goal rate, advance to goal over 2-3 days. Monitor glucose q6h initially. Add insulin to bag if needed."
